      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CORLESS DEVIOUS (5) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Has hit the frame at his last four runs, the latest finishing third (23.26) at Richmond. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Expected to feature in the finish again. SCOTT QUIBBLE (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (23.24) in a Grade 5 at The Gardens. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. Can do much better this time. GLORIFIED (8) made light work of the tricky draw with a scorching early sectional but swamped late when a close up fifth (21.10) at Nowra over 365m. Comes out of a hot form race last start. Likely to play a prominent role. JET'S DIGGER (7) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
